layout record Header:
  tag: u8
  length: u16
  flags: u8

parse header bytes: buffer of (size of Header) u8 gives i32:
  check length of bytes is equal to size of Header
  let header be read Header from bytes at 0
  header.tag as i32

main gives i32:
  let bytes be buffer of (size of Header) u8 filled with 0
  bytes at 0 becomes 7
  parse header bytes
